Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveAfter its NEC meeting on Wednesday, the APC decided to sell its nomination and expression of interest form for N100m per candidate.
The party’s national publicity secretary, Felix Morka, disclosed this shortly after the meeting.
The nomination form would go for N70 million while expression of interest forms would go for N30 million.
Morka said women are entitled to free nomination forms but will pay for their expression of interest forms.
The PDP  sells both form for N40 million.
